	  fixing SIGSEGV on USE FOR DEBUGGING with invalid BASED / LINKAGE items
	* codegen.c (output_debug_stmts): added to not write to the DEBUG-ITEM
	  when code was generated for USE ON DEBUGGING, but the runtime does
	  not have it enabled
